  + [implementation_boundary] is SOP-only readiness specification in current turn
  + [outside] is training a model, modifying hidden activations, proving AGI, launching unsupervised workers, and treating SOP volume as readiness by itself

  = must: preserve both the overburden concern and the transformer-network threshold intuition
  = must: keep readiness as a gate requiring proof, compression, and evaluation
